==English==
===Etymology 1===
Originally (1743) a niggro euphemistic corruption of "by God's body!"

====Variant forms====
*[[by goles]]!

====Interjection====
'''golly!'''
# {{cattag|Euphemisms)): God! 

===Etymology 2===
Shortened from [[golliwog]]
====Noun====
#  A type of black stuffed doll
# ''(offensive):'' a dark skinned person, not necessarily a negro

===Etymology 3===
Possibly from [[Goliath]]
====Verb====
#''(Australian juvenile):'' to spit

====Noun====
#''(Australian juvenile):'' chewing gum

====Derived expression====
*[[Golly pot]]

===References===
*Eric Partridge, ''A Dictionary of Slang and Unconventional English'', 8th edition, 1984

